            "title": "智邦AI需求旺 5月營收182億元再創新高",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>網通廠智邦今 (5) 日公告 5 月營收達 180 億元，呈年月雙增，再創單月營收新高；累計前 5 月營收達 788.1 億元，年增 127.5%；智邦表示，此次營收成長緣由為客戶需求增加。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" class=\"cr8g41v\" data-nimg=\"fill\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"\n            (max-width: 1024px) 100% 406px,\n            (max-width: 768px) 100% 193px\n          \" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008310%2Fl%2F0e29a0c20dd83ba6ff6380a1fe89d942.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008310%2Fl%2F0e29a0c20dd83ba6ff6380a1fe89d942.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008310%2Fl%2F0e29a0c20dd83ba6ff6380a1fe89d942.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008310%2Fl%2F0e29a0c20dd83ba6ff6380a1fe89d942.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008310%2Fl%2F0e29a0c20dd83ba6ff6380a1fe89d942.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008310%2Fl%2F0e29a0c20dd83ba6ff6380a1fe89d942.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008310%2Fl%2F0e29a0c20dd83ba6ff6380a1fe89d942.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008310%2Fl%2F0e29a0c20dd83ba6ff6380a1fe89d942.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008310%2Fl%2F0e29a0c20dd83ba6ff6380a1fe89d942.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008310%2Fl%2F0e29a0c20dd83ba6ff6380a1fe89d942.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008310%2Fl%2F0e29a0c20dd83ba6ff6380a1fe89d942.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008310%2Fl%2F0e29a0c20dd83ba6ff6380a1fe89d942.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008310%2Fl%2F0e29a0c20dd83ba6ff6380a1fe89d942.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008310%2Fl%2F0e29a0c20dd83ba6ff6380a1fe89d942.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008310%2Fl%2F0e29a0c20dd83ba6ff6380a1fe89d942.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008310%2Fl%2F0e29a0c20dd83ba6ff6380a1fe89d942.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008310%2Fl%2F0e29a0c20dd83ba6ff6380a1fe89d942.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">智邦5月營收182億元再創新高 AI需求旺持續出貨。(圖：shutterstock)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>智邦 5 月營收 182.8 億元，月增 2.8%，年增 108.3%；累計前 5 月營收 788.12 億元，年增 127.5%。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>智邦受惠於資料中心需求，第一季獲利走強，並獲美系外資點讚，表示 AI 加速器及 400G 交換器帶動下，看好第二季營收表現；智邦在資料中心升級需求下，800G 產品出貨暢旺，而最新型 1.6T 交換器，目前由客戶驗證中，市場預期最晚於明年上半年出貨。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
